description: Demolition of existing residential building and the construction of a new part-two, part-three, part-seven and part-eight storey building comprising 133 residential flats (class C3) (including 48 'extra care' flats with ancillary communal facilities) and 6 two and three-storey houses (class C3), together with the construction of a new road (comprising the relocation of Lidcote Gardens linking Robsart Street and Denchworth House Place), 2 surface level drop-off parking bays adjacent to Robsart Street and a vehicular access from this new road to a basement car park providing 46 car parking spaces and 139 cycle parking spaces.
